Comment: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:02.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,chapter,Part B
Comment: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:40.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,chapter,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:09.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Is an athlete an athlete \Nfrom the day they are born?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:12.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What about an astronaut or an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You can't know what you'll be at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Then... what about witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm just about finished with my laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It'll go back to normal soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,This spring is touched by magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's beautiful every time I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:03.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Magic is so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:12.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world brims with magic, \Nan essential and handy miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:17.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But how it works is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Witches are the only ones\Nwho can cast spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:28.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}and ordinary people can \Nonly be blessed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not everyone can become a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Must be nice being born a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,O sheets, O sheets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:50.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I command you to turn \Ninto a flying cloak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:56.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant by "flying"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's a pegasus carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I've never seen one land before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:39.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom! There's a pegasus carriage outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I didn't know you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's on me \Nfor standing by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,Oh, my. I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,Look! Who'd have thought this place \Nwould have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer B,0,0,0,,Oh, but isn't wood-sorrel \Nembroidery a bit dated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer A,0,0,0,,You won't believe what I found! \NThis is Harrian lace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:14.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,Oh, amazing! It sold out \Nin no time in the castle town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:17.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer A,0,0,0,,{\an8}We were right to travel \Nall this way by pegasus carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,They're the people who came \Nin the pegasus carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm not with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Do you have \Nany more lace like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Yes, certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look, this one's so cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Coco, don't just stand there. \NHelp out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,{\an8}How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Sir, what can we help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I'm looking for some smoke-colored fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,But I can come back later if you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can take care of the cutting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,She's got a good handle on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer B,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Can I go see the \Npegasus carriage after I'm done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,There's a pegasus carriage outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,A pegasus carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,You'd better not be thinking of \Nmessing with the customers' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm just gonna look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I won't say I want to be a witch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,If you finish up early, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting. \NWhat are the measurements?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Oh, I wrote it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:00.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You've got great concentration, steady hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,No hesitation in the line, clean cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,And such a careful, precise finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:15.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I had no idea this village had \Nsuch a skilled craftsperson. {A wheel was spun to decide if we make my bisexual(?) icon woke or not. Hopefully you can guess the result.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,This is real magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:24.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,N-N-N-N-N-N-N-No! \NIt's nothing like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Magic is way more mysterious and sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's valuable and really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,And it's something that's more... more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:36.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Something truly p-precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You really like magic, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Mind if I ask why you like it so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:56.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,When I was little, \NI went to a festival at the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:00.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,and I met a witch wearing a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy \Na magic picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:31.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I love picture books, but what's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:36.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,Magic is a miracle \Nthat makes this world vibrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,A pegasus carriage \Nthat soars through the vast sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:43.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,an everlasting spring \Nthat preserves crystal-clear waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,Even the cobblestones beneath your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,lighting up as you walk—it's all magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,So pwetty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch,0,0,0,,It comes with a free wand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,And you ended up buying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,But you said you wanted \Nthe roasted strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:15.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,When I followed a butterfly, \Nthere was a person with a pointed hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,You already told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:21.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,So it's a magical picture book! \NWith a wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Okay, then. Let's head home, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:34.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm gonna be a witch \Nthat makes our world vibrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Listen, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:45.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,You can't become a witch unless \Nyou're born with magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Ordinary people don't have \Nwhat it takes to be a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The ground shines \Nevery time I take a step!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:05.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,If the ground shines all the way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:08.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,then maybe you'll be \Nable to use magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Since then, I've sort of \Ngrown fond of watching magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can't let go of my dream \Nof becoming a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Could you tell me a little more about—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.35,GJM_Main_1080p,All,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:29.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Handler,0,0,0,,Hey, now, settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Handler,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,Look what you've done. Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,Shut up... Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,We didn't do anything. \NIt fell apart on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,Liar! You crawled underneath it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,You snitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,He hit his head, and it fell over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer A,0,0,0,,Oh, my! How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer A,0,0,0,,Look what you've done \Nto our pegasus carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer B,0,0,0,,It was our father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:12.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry for the awful \Ntrouble they've caused you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer B,0,0,0,,A-Apologizing won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer C,0,0,0,,We can't go back home without a carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Oh, my... What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Would you like me to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:28.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,From what I can see, \Nthe damage isn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer,0,0,0,,And who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,My apologies. It would help \Nif I had my signature hat on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,My name is Qifrey. I am a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Both,0,0,0,,The pointed hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer,0,0,0,,So you can fix our carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Handler,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver, Mr. Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I'll just reapply the spell \Nto the carriage's floorboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Customer A,0,0,0,,We'd love to ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,At your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:05.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,However, doing it outdoors \Nmight be a bit—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You can use our workshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:08.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Hey, Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Come on, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:16.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a real witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be my chance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}to see the exact moment \Nof a spell being cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:34.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Will you keep watch outside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:38.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,and make sure no one looks \Nin while I'm casting the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:41.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \Ndon't let anyone come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Life isn't that easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why can't we watch how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic is all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet we don't know how it's cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Witches are the only ones \Nwho know the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,She found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,She's nothing. We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,Can we see the room from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,Lower your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Move over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:40.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Tanerl,0,0,0,,Bleh, no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Kamla,0,0,0,,Seriously, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I really wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,He's drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,He's drawing magic with a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:09.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Then... that wasn't a wand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:15.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Spells aren't something you cast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,but something you draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,I'm a bit relieved, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,You love magic so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:04.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,so I thought you'd say you \Nwanted to go with that witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,I lost your father to illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:13.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,So if you left me too, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I won't! I won't leave you \Nby yourself, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Thanks. You're such a sweet girl, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Oh, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Never mind. Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,I thought you'd say you \Nwanted to go with that witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}The patterns drawn all over \Nthe magic picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wand wasn't just a bonus \Nthat came with the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pen itself was the magic wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Mom... I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just let me try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Bummer, nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Yeah, it couldn't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It sparkled! I actually used magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:24.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wow, magic! I used magic! Real magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It worked! Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,So magic {\i1}is{\i0} something you draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:31.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But I wasn't supposed to see it. \NWill he get mad if he finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But let's draw one more. Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}A picture book... A picture book, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}It bugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wow! That one was a fire spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No, stop burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting \Nto get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Bigger ones are stronger \Nthan smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,And neatly drawn ones \Nlast longer than sloppy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But drawing it big and neat is so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:33.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,That man made it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:45.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can draw it neatly \Nby tracing over the example.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You drew magic, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:21.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,What did you draw?! \NWhat kind of spell did you draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I don't know. I just traced the pattern \Nthat was in the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's mom,0,0,0,,Coco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is... forbidden magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,No! You'll get caught up in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I have to save my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's no use! It's a spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,And an evil one—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:10.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Of course you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:24.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It was kept a secret so \Nnothing like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,A special ink and a set of Casting Seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's all anyone needs to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's the One Great Rule of witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:39.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,And now that you've found out, \NI must erase your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:48.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,If I forget everything, \Nwho will save my mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I don't remember what \Nkind of magic I drew,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:56.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,but I know what was written \Nin the picture book by heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,And if I forget that, my mom is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:06.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that picture book belonged to {\i0}them{\i1}, \NI'll be losing track of their whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:11.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have no way to trace them \Nif I erase her memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:14.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}You remember the book by heart, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}And which page you copied?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:24.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh! If we can find the same book, \Nwe can find the Casting Seal I drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:31.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Can we save my mom if we find \Nwhich Casting Seal it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:35.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:37.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:38.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mr. Qifrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:45.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Please don't erase my memories! \NI'll do anything to save my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Can you keep the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Are you willing to learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Learn... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:59.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Once you know the truth, \Nit can't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,In that case, you must become \None of those who know the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:06.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That is the only way for you \Nto keep your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:09.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:10.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:14.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,you are going to become a witch.
